  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Lakshadweep</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Lakshadweep has a tropical maritime climate — warm and humid year-round (25–32°C). October to May is the best period — calm seas and superb diving visibility (40m+). The southwest monsoon (June–September) brings heavy rain and rough seas that make inter-island travel impossible. Peak season is December–March when the lagoons are at their clearest and calmest.</p>
